scopecontent.p:
Making longer words by adding endings; ed, three 
		ways of pronouncing ed; ed as in lifted, d as in called, and t as in talked; 
		ed when following d or t; d when it follows voiced letters, b, e, g, j, 1, m, n, 
		o, r, v, n, y, z; t when it follows unvoiced letters, ch, f, k, p, sh, x, ss; 
		quiz.
